s |title=Windows Phone 8.0 is upgradeable, Microsoft says - Computerworld<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2014-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820160253/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9245273/Windows_Phone_8.0_is_upgradeable_Microsoft_says |dead-url=no }}</ref>

