==歷史==
Windows Phone 8.1是与[[Windows_8.1|Windows 8.1]]相对应的手机操作系统，最开始有谣言称Windows Phone 8.1名为“Windows Phone Blue”。虽然微软原本计划在2013年秋季发布WP8.1，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/3/3/4059922/windows-phone-next-release-due-holiday-2013 |title=Microsoft says 'next release' of Windows Phone is on target for the holidays {{!}} The Verge<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511095912/https://www.theverge.com/2013/3/3/4059922/windows-phone-next-release-due-holiday-2013 }}</ref>但是该系统的普遍推送被推迟到了2014年春。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/7/12/4516894/microsoft-windows-phone-8-updates/in/4584231 |title=Microsoft details new Windows Phone 8 update, but real fixes won't come until 2014 {{!}} The Verge<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511095912/https://www.theverge.com/2013/7/12/4516894/microsoft-windows-phone-8-updates/in/4584231 }}</ref>为了在长达一年的Windows 8与8.1的产品周期间隙中保持产品活力，微软分别于2012年12月、2013年7月和2013年10月发布了更新，更新中整合了多项新功能和优化，旨在为Windows 8.1的发布做基础；其中包括了为非[[Verizon|Verizon]]设备提供的新功能DataSense，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://winsupersite.com/windows-phone/complete-guide-windows-phone-8-gdr2 |title=Complete Guide to Windows Phone 8 GDR2 {{!}} Windows Phone content from Paul Thurrott's SuperSite for Windows<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2013-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006165950/http://winsupersite.com/windows-phone/complete-guide-windows-phone-8-gdr2 }}</ref>并增强了对多核处理器及高清屏幕设备的支持，以及“驾驶模式”的推出和为“平板手机”提供的优化。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pocketnow.com/2013/10/14/microsoft-windows-phone-8-gdr3-update-detailed |title=Microsoft Windows Phone 8 GDR3 update detailed {{!}} Pocketnow<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2016-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415060931/http://pocketnow.com/2013/10/14/microsoft-windows-phone-8-gdr3-update-detailed |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

操作系统的最终于2014年2月10日，在微软为开发者提供Windows Phone 8.1 SDK后，正式与公众见面。<ref name="WPCentral2"/>SDK发布数小时内，相关谍照就公诸于世了。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mashable.com/2014/02/10/windows-phone-8-1-update-notification-center/ |title=Leaked Photos of Windows Phone 8.1 Update Reveal Notification Center<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2021-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608060535/https://mashable.com/2014/02/10/windows-phone-8-1-update-notification-center/ }}</ref>

Windows Phone 8.1的开发者预览版于2014年4月14日发布，并作为Beta版本放出下载。<ref name="preview"/>

===Update 1===
Update 1 于在2014年8月4日推送到参加 Windows Phone 开发者预览版本程序的用户，<ref>,http://techcrunch.com/2014/08/04/windows-phone-8-1-update-1-goes-live-for-developers/ {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/08/04/windows-phone-8-1-update-1-goes-live-for-developers/ |date=20211010095625 }}</ref>是2014年 Windows Phone 8.1 两次<ref>{{cite web |last=Rubino |first=Daniel |url=http://www.wpcentral.com/windows-phone-81-two-os-updates-2014 |title=Windows Phone 8.1 to get at least two OS updates in 2014 | Windows Phone Central |publisher=Wpcentral.com |date=2014-04-07 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archive-date=2014-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018101443/http://www.wpcentral.com/windows-phone-81-two-os-updates-2014 }}</ref>主要更新的第一次。它为 cortana 添加了新的语言和区域支持，用于开始屏幕组织整理应用的文件夹、短信转发的多个消息、改进 Xbox Music ， Windows Phone 商店的支持动态磁贴及可以测试应用的应用园地。微软已改变 Internet Explorer Mobile ，使其带来的浏览器体验更接近 Safari （iOS） 和 Chrome （Android）。要做到这一点，微软远离了开放标准并采用在 Safari 和 Chrome 中使用的非标准特性，实现浏览器检测，改善检测到的使用旧式 WebKit 特征页面的渲染、带来HTML 5的支持，修复与错误 HTML 代码<ref>{{cite web |author=Jul 31, 2014 Paul Thurrott |url=http://winsupersite.com/windows-phone/windows-phone-81-update-1-internet-explorer |title=Windows Phone 8.1 Update 1: Internet Explorer | Windows Phone content from Paul Thurrott's SuperSite for Windows |publisher=Winsupersite.com |date=2014-07-31 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808065701/http://winsupersite.com/windows-phone/windows-phone-81-update-1-internet-explorer |archive-date=2014-08-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>的互操作性问题。此外，Update 1 还包括新的 VPN 和蓝牙功能，对于企业用户，支持互动的保护套，如 HTC 的"Dot View"保护套、 更大的"平板"屏幕分辨率如 1280 x 800 、 540 x 960 qHD屏和 1280 x 768 和高通 QuickCharge 2.0 标准。<ref>{{cite web |last=Belfiore |first=Joe |url=http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/windowsphone/archive/2014/07/30/windows-phone-8-1-update-brings-cortana-to-new-markets-new-features.aspx |title=Windows Phone 8.1 Update brings Cortana to new markets + new featuresBlogging Windows |publisher=Blogs.windows.com |date=2014-07-30 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archive-date=2014-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730123306/http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/windowsphone/archive/2014/07/30/windows-phone-8-1-update-brings-cortana-to-new-markets-new-features.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="WPCentral_8.1Update1">{{cite web |last=Rubino |first=Daniel |url=http://www.wpcentral.com/official-update-1-windows-phone-81-next-week-preview |title=Microsoft reveals Update 1 for Windows Phone 8.1, due next week for Preview users | Windows Phone Central |publisher=Wpcentral.com |date=2014-07-30 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archive-date=2014-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825212955/http://www.wpcentral.com/official-update-1-windows-phone-81-next-week-preview |dead-url=no }}</ref>它也移除了部分市场默认搜索提供商选择谷歌的选项。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digit.in/mobile-phones/windows-phone-81-gdr1-update-removes-google-search-in-uosome-markets-23480.html |title=Windows Phone 8.1 GDR1 update removes Google search in some markets {{!}} Digit.in |access-date=2015-05-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308065820/http://www.digit.in/mobile-phones/windows-phone-81-gdr1-update-removes-google-search-in-uosome-markets-23480.html }}</ref>

===Update 2===
